name: Eye of the Tiger (white)
description:
White Fitted T-Shirt

100% Ringspun combed cotton
Features soft front print with waterbased ink

The Tiger is a fearsome beast with those beautiful yet captivating Eyes.   

We recommend that you machine wash cold with like colours and hang dry the t-shirt.
Do not tumble dry
Do not iron on the prints
